[Student "S"]
{SOUTH has 14 points and opens her 4-card \C suit.

NORTH must respond, and with two 4-card Majors bids them "up-the-line", saying 1\H.

SOUTH now shows his 4-card \S suit, and NORTH again must bid. Since NORTH is pretty weak he just 
raises to 2\S, which SOUTH happily passes.}

